{"tid":13773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上月旅客跌幅收窄 中國客續減國際過夜客升3.1%☺️","createTime":"2016-11-30T08:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:25:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"187ef8337516f11ecd01ad3674cf93e936f08dde","tid":13773,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"旅發局公佈10月份訪港旅客數字，按年下跌2.4%至495萬人次，跌幅比9月份的3%稍為收窄，其中內地客按年跌3.5%，而今年首10個月累積訪港旅客按年下跌5.7%。<br />\n<br />\n10月份國際訪港旅客則按月錄得1.1%升幅至122萬人次，其中印尼升18.1%至36,672人，菲律賓升9.4%至68,458人，國際過夜旅客亦有3.1%增長。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局指今年加大力度於短途市場推廣，其中南韓、印尼及菲律賓的過夜旅客增長均達到雙位數字，會繼續聯同航空公司、本地酒店及主要景點、海外業界等，於內地和短途巿場，合作推出以家庭及年青客群為主要對象的優惠遊港產品，同時亦會向旅客及國際傳媒推廣冬日節慶活動，希望吸引更多過夜旅客來港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55985578&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55985578%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=11d4fc79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55985578%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&h=a8693b98\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55985578&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130</a>"},{"pid":"1b3196fa0310878e7258c2a1d764ba298a610f82","tid":13773,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"吸引多D外國遊客先係正路"},{"pid":"47427404e5b3a2ea89f82a8f84ed4f401fccc4ac","tid":13773,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae05ee0e5da40469099191d0ea7309c2c97b7bb","t